{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "糟糕……天黑了呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "虽然想在入夜前回到城堡，\\n不过看来不容易呢……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110037_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "如果打算露宿，还是拉倒吧。\\n这一带的荒野很危险。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110037_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "我带你去附近的城镇吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "噢！\\n看来你总算也有\\n为伙伴着想的心啦！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110037_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "带路费\\n我会另收的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "呜……\\n就不该对你改观的……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "刀刃钝了很多……\\n我去打磨一下武器。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110037_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "这样的话，\\n去大路后面的铁匠铺比较好。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110037_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "虽然有点贵，但技术有保障。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "尤蒂尔！\\n我去采购\\n明天要用的水和食材。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110037_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "那我推荐小巷的路边摊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110037_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "这个时间也还在营业，\\n而且水果新鲜又好吃。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "伊尔凡，你对这个城镇\\n真是了如指掌。经常来吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110037_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "还行吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110037_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "我们一族虽没有土地，\\n但为了行商，会来镇上落脚。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110037_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "出售狩猎时获得的肉跟毛皮，\\n用赚来的钱买武器和医疗用品。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110037_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "从以前就受到这镇子许多关照。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "没有栖身之地的一族……吗。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "可是，没关系吗？\\n你说过这一带很危险吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "而且最近魔兽也变多了。\\n住在郊外很危险吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110037_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "关于这个……嗯，没错。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110037_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "因为受到魔兽袭击，\\n族人数量日渐减少。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "就算只有一阵子也好，\\n找个哪里的城镇\\n避难一下比较好吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110037_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "是啊，我也这么认为。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110037_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "可是族人的骄傲，\\n不容许自己依赖他国的庇护。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110037_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "与其受人保护，宁可选择死亡。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110037_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "我们一族，\\n从以前就是这样活过来的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110037_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "我也不是要他们舍弃骄傲，\\n但是……也没有必要墨守成规，\\n抱着骄傲走向灭亡吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110037_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "我讨厌我们族内迂腐的规矩，\\n所以一直采纳新事物，\\n努力尝试改变。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110037_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "还试着离开族人生活，\\n现在穿的这件衣服，\\n也是王都中流行的最新款式。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110037_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "但不管我自身怎么改变，\\n族人们仍被老旧的规矩束缚着。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110037_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "身为族长的长子，实在无法坐视不管。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这样啊……那真令人担心呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "就没有什么可以让你的族人\\n平安度日的方法吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110037_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "倒也不是没有主意。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110037_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "由我来建一座城镇就好了。\\n由族人管理、属于我们一族的城镇。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110037_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "这样一来，族人们应该\\n也会同意居住在城镇了吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110037_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "但是，那需要庞大的资金……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "咦，难道你一直\\n那么执着于金钱是为了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110037_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "说漏嘴了。\\n刚才那些话当我没说过，忘了吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这样啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我懂了。你不想说的话，\\n我就不再问了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "但是……我要说一句。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我觉得为族人奋战的你……\\n非常了不起。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110037_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "少、少废话！\\n我不是叫你忘掉吗！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}